description: This file serves as the entry point for a React application. It imports necessary modules, sets up the root rendering of the React component tree, and initiates rendering within the DOM element with ID 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root React node for rendering. Part of React DOM server-side rendering API.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM.
